<![CDATA[<p>They must be doing some really crazy stuff with JavaScript to get it to work (notice how neither the parent nor the nested anchor tags have a name or href attribute - all functionality is done through the class name and JS).</p><br/><br/><p>Here is what the html looks like:</p><br/><br/><pre><code>&lt;a class="page_tab page_tab"&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class="page_title" title="Click to rename this page."&gt;Click &amp; Type Page Name&lt;/div&gt;<br/>  &lt;a class="delete_page" title="Click to delete this page" style="display: block;"&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;<br/>&lt;/a&gt;<br/></code></pre><br/>]]>    </template>
